title: Bengals letting star DE Hendrickson seek trade

title: Jaguars trading WR Kirk to Texans, source says
description: The Jaguars are trading wide receiver Christian Kirk to the Texans for a 2026 seventh-round pick, a source told ESPN's Adam Schefter on Thursday.
author: ESPN

description: Luke Littler wins night five of the Premier League in Brighton on an evening which sees two nine-dart finishes.

description: Luke Littler reigned supreme with a 6-3 win over Nathan Aspinall on a memorable Premier League night where Luke Humphries and Rob Cross both hit nine-darters to ignite the Brighton crowd.

title: 'Good result!' - Jose says tie not over despite 'punishment' in Rangers defeat
description: Jose Mourinho has described Fenerbahce's shock 3-1 Europa League loss to Rangers as "a good result" but insisted their last-16 encounter is not over.
